50|$|Many {{unofficial}} garments and <b>helmet</b> <b>covers</b> {{were produced}} as field expedients or were tailor-made, mostly from zeltbahn material. These included {{versions of the}} service dress uniform, parachute-jump smocks, field jackets, rucksacks and panzer jackets. Later materials included rayon.|$|E
